OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDon't call us the Blob,    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Furges top civil servant    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK's top official has called on    
OL,6, politicians to stop referring to the   
OL,7, Civil Service as "the Blob", calling   
OL,8, the term "insulting".                  
OL,10,FSimon Case told MPs he was not aware of
OL,11,Fany current ministers using the term,  
OL,12,Fwhich he added was "dehumanising".     
OL,14,FBut he said attacks on civil servants  
OL,15,Fby "significant political figures" had 
OL,16,Fincreased in recent years.             
OL,18,FHe added it was part of a wider trend  
OL,19,Ftowards more "vindictive" language in  
OL,20,Fpolitical debate.                      
